description.en: BabySatoshi is the newest member of the Nakamoto family based on the Ethereum network. To celebrate his arrival, holders of $bSatoshi receive an 8% redistribution in Bitcoin as a percentage of each network transaction. The Baby Satoshi contract is the first of it’s kind as an ERC-20 token offering Bitcoin rewards. By encouraging volume and holding a larger amount of supply, Baby Satoshi is built for the community.
